Privacy Policy
Personal Information
Store Connect for Shopify does not require its customers to provide any personal information. The only exception is
            your
            email address which is required to create a Store Connect for Shopify account in case if you want to enjoy its
            benefits.
Your email will not be shared with any 3rd parties and will be used only to communicate
            with you.
Anonymous Information
Store Connect for Shopify collects anonymous data about your device that does not directly identify you, such as:
            version
            of the app, version of the operating system you are running, system language, timezone. This information
            is used solely for the purpose of improving our services and is not shared with any 3rd parties.
Account Deletion
You can delete your Store Connect for Shopify account by submitting a request through the app support.
Store Connect for Shopify Email
Store Connect for Shopify Email service is a separate service which allows you to forward emails from
            merchants/carriers to
            your unique email address in order for the tracking numbers in these emails to be automatically
            recognized and added to your Store Connect for Shopify Account.
Emails received from you this way are kept
            indefinitely for the purpose of improving our services. Emails are not shared with any 3rd parties.
Contact Us
Please feel free to
contact us
in case if you have any
            questions.